latestIgtvVideos.title: Happy birthday Bestie✨
latestIgtvVideos.caption: My best friend, my kutte, paglal ladka. Love you soo so much. Thank you for always being there for me . While others made me cry, u were the one who made me laugh harder. 🥺Today, i dont know why, but i cant express myself. U have done so much for me!Fought for me, motivated me when i wanted to give up , supported me. You have been an inspiration to me akki. From you, i have learnt to deal with situations, i have learnt to focus on my goals. I wish and pray that this bond and this friendship never ends! I dont know about the future, but all i know is that I dont wanna lose you ever! You mean so much to me.❤️🥰💖🥺🥺🥺💝💝💕💞💘💓💗
